{"tid":1888282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當香港人仲掛住排口罩 搶廁紙 討論邊個邊個ig女神 (2)","createTime":"2020-02-20T06:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T07:45:56.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f676f54cc692934bdc259d9c33a3e8038c20ee7","tid":1888282,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T06:02:43.000Z","msg":"代開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日幾多號呀各位 <br />\n2.21啊 <br />\n721恐佈襲擊    7個月<br />\n但而家成個熱門一個721post 都冇？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3TnV16y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3TnV16y.jpg&h=7357fac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個熱門根本不知所謂 <br />\n特別係而家仲有心情討論咩ig 女神嗰班人<br />\n香港人唔好再掛住排口罩 搶廁紙啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lhn3rBL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhn3rBL.gif&h=0fd161f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家黨鐵聽日站都唔撚封<br />\n雖然我依家講可能有啲早<br />\n但係好明顯佢哋都係睇死我哋香港人唔記得721<br />\n今日先有兩個手足 以行為藝術方式跪低 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MsbAqD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MsbAqD.png&h=8440e333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就係希望你哋唔好忘記死去同在囚嘅手足 <br />\n希望你唔好忘記初心 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我相信 香港人 面對肺炎<br />\n依然毋忘初心</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">221</span></strong></span><br />\n大西北人 元朗黨鐵站見<br />\n其他香港人 唔方便就各大黨鐵站見<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/384hvW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F384hvW5.jpg&h=0202158a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9srphr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9srphr.jpg&h=4a3edbd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5pasTaN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5pasTaN.jpg&h=d3f8951a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nP牌仔求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cfa4c367096aa183da2b42bc08fc928a5f152a","t